  title `Page 3`
  content obj_root_law_sections_3_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes
  sourcePage 3
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line 3
  line SCHEDULE
  line `FORM NO. 1.`
  line `Form No. 1.`
  line `N OTICE is hereby given by the Collector of Land - revenue in Bombay, under Act XI. of 1853, that`
  line `( describe the encroachment ) is to be removed or abated within one month from the date hereof; otherwise`
  line `the same will be removed or abated by the said Collector under the authority of the said Act.Dated`
  line `the day of in the year of our Lord`
  line `( Signature of Collector. )`
  line _________
  line `Form No. 2.`
  line `This W arrant, granted by the Collector of Lan d - revenue in Bombay, under Act XI. of 1853, is to`
  line `authorize of to remove ( describe encroachment ).`
  line `Dated ( Signature of Collector.)`
  line ———
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line
